### 用戶註冊與登入流程 (HTTP)

# 註冊
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 登入
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}
